data.description: Move in Ready Home!! Welcome home to this turn-key property located on a spacious 5000 SF lot in the heart of Richmond's North & East neighborhood! This fully remodeled home boasts 3 generous bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, inviting covered front porch, large backyard with patio and lots of nice shade & fruit trees, plus a large detached 2-car garage with an EV charge port - or convert the garage to an ADU.  Enjoy full-size laundry hookups, a fully upgraded kitchen with a stainless 5-burner gas range and quartz countertops. This move in ready home combines modern amenities with classic charm and gets tons of natural sunlight. Parking at this home is a huge bonus and this home's long driveway is large enough to fit 3-4 cars tandem or even your RV + the 2 spots in the garage! Richmond's North & East community is home to Wendell Playground, Berg Park (lots of community events), Catahoula Coffee, Tacos El Tucan, and Richmond Art Center with tons of classes. Join lively Halloween festivities, enjoy pet-friendly spaces, and embrace the tight nit community vibe. Proximity to parks, beaches, and the city makes the location a great choice for convenience
